               <msContents>
                  <summary/>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i0">
                     <locus from="2r" to="230v">2r-230v</locus>
                     <textLang xml:lang="ar">Arabic</textLang>
                     <title type="acephalous apodous lacunous" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT0049IHA">قران</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#2r">-2r</locus>ان مثل عيسى عند الله كمثل آدم خلقه من تراب ثم قال له كن فيكون</incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#230v">-230v</locus>ان هو الا ذكر للعلمين</explicit>
                     <note>The text begins with verse 3:59 and ends with verse 81:27. Fol. 230 is bound the wrong way as fol. 230r contains the headings of sūras 82 and 83, whereas fol. 230v contains the heading of sūra 81. Text in the upper part of fols 49-107 smudged due to damp. Vocalized. Words divided into two lines. Ṯumn markers.</note>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
